OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNew acting chairwoman of   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FBBC announced              
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Dame Elan Closs Stephens has been      
OL,6, appointed as acting chairwoman of the  
OL,7, BBC after Richard Sharp's resignation. 
OL,9,FHe stepped down earlier this year after
OL,10,Fbreaking rules over dealings with      
OL,11,Fthen-PM Boris Johnson ahead of his     
OL,12,Fappointment.                           
OL,14,FDame Elan will lead the BBC board from 
OL,15,F27 June for 12 months or until a new   
OL,16,Fpermanent chair has been appointed,    
OL,17,Fwhichever is sooner.                   
OL,19,FShe said the new role was "a huge      
OL,20,Fhonour".                               
